ivardefs.name: dateWritten
ivardefs.desc: The date (and perhaps time) when the prescription was written.

ivardefs.name: dispense_
ivardefs.desc: Deals with details of the dispense part of the supply specification.

ivardefs.name: encounter
ivardefs.desc: A link to a resource that identifies the particular occurrence of contact between patient and health care provider.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifier which may be used by other parties to reference or identify the prescription.

ivardefs.name: patient
ivardefs.desc: A link to a resource representing the person to whom the vision products will be supplied.

ivardefs.name: prescriber
ivardefs.desc: The healthcare professional responsible for authorizing the prescription.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of the resource instance.
